Class Fraction

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
civitas.celestis.math.Fraction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Number>
public class Fraction extends Number implements Comparable<Number>
A mathematical fraction with a numerator n and a denominator d.
